lead_paragraph: Defending champion Nao Hibino reached the semifinals of the Tashkent Open on Thursday, advancing when Lesia Tsurenko retired after losing the first set 7-6 (6).

headline.print_headline: 4th-Seeded Nao Hibino Advances to Tashkent Open Semifinals
